oking\r\n<ul class=\"case-studies-no-bullets\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Define pick-up points</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Select cab type</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">See all available cabs near defined pick-up points</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Select date and time of pick up</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Book your ride</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Get instant confirmation with driver details</div></li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div class=\"hyphen\">--</div>\r\n<div class=\"solutionOfferingscontent\">Pay on completion of the ride</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Pick up location is Auto detected through GPS. This can be modified by navigating on the map, tapping the address bar or selecting from favorites</li>\r\n 	<li>Track statuses real-time by viewing the driver reach your pick-up location. You can also track your own journey while moving from one location to the other</li>\r\n 	<li>Check booking history  completed rides / Advance booking instantly</li>\r\n 	<li>Check user profile details on-the-go</li>\r\n 	<li>Rate the Driver</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"pad-top-10p\">Service provider side application capabilities:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"case-studies-bulls\">\r\n 	<li>User profile creation / modifications</li>\r\n 	<li>Call support</li>\r\n 	<li>Social media integration</li>\r\n 	<li>My e-wallet option (optional)</li>\r\n 	<li>Book a ride for your friend (optional)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"pad-top-10p\">Driver side application capabilities:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"case-studies-bulls\">\r\n 	<li>Initiate the ride</li>\r\n 	<li>Close the ride  after confirming the payments</li>\r\n 	<li>Rate the user</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\r\n<div class=\"panel-heading beas-accordian tech_platform_block accordion-toggle\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion2\" data-target=\"#collapseFourCase3\">\r\n<h4 class=\"panel-title\">Solution Benefits</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"collapseFourCase3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\">\r\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n\r\nThe solution offers the following benefits:\r\n<ul class=\"case-studies-bulls\">\r\n 	<li>Locates cab based on GPS locator</li>\r\n 	<li>Ensures ease of use in Booking or cancelling cabs</li>\r\n 	<li>Reduces waiting time</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides Push notification facilities for booking or cancellation</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic calculation of cab fare</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides facilities to Rate the driver and service</li>\r\n 	<li>Optimizes route planning for the cab drivers by identifying the pickup spot and destination place early</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides flexible payment method via credit card/wallet or cash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--accordian end-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div title=\"eighth page Title\"><img src=\"http://beas.in/iclipse/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3-case-study.png\" alt=\"Fleet Management System (FMS)\" width=\"534\" height=\"540\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-58\" /></div>\r\n<div title=\"nineth page Title\">\r\n\r\n<!--accordian-->\r\n<div class=\"page_row\">\r\n<h3>Mobile Application On Fleet Management System (FMS)</h3>\r\n<div id=\"accordion3\" class=\"panel-group\">\r\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\r\n<div class=\"panel-heading business_need_block beas-accordian accordion-toggle\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapseOneCase4\" data-parent=\"#accordion3\">\r\n<h4 class=\"panel-title\">Solution Description</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"collapseOneCase4\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n<div class=\"panel-body\">Lorem 